HEADWORD: Jingling
<hw>Jin"gling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process
of producing a jingle; also, the sound itself; a chink.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>jingling</xex> of the guinea.⟦rdquo⟧
